<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrīḥ § tātaśrīnagarīti dikṣudaśasu khyōtābhiyānē purēcakrē <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> </hi>
<lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha">draṇapaṇḍita stadakhilakṣmāmaṇḍanam maṇḍapam § Addhyāsapriyyāsamam ka</hi>
<lb n="3"/><hi rend="grantha">malayā sukrīḍamānō harissadyassāgaramaddhyavāsa janitaujāḍyaujahautā draśam</hi>
<lb n="4"/><hi rend="grantha">bhavati nagarināthasyāthasthitādipatē harē payamihabhuvisthāna nityāsikāvi</hi>
<lb n="5" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">dhayē param ma</hi><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">ḻa</seg><hi rend="grantha">vanrapatēścēta stātasya bhaktiparāyaṇantadupa</hi>
<lb n="6" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">racitacētrākāra maṇḍapamucbhritam § kavipitāmhasya §</hi>
</p>

